[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "本劇情涉及活動劇情「失落的信仰～前篇～」與「失落的信仰～後篇～」的核心內容。", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0072.wav"], "content": "簽好了。也麻煩你簽名。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "我知道了。簽這裡就好嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "嗯。抱歉給你添麻煩了。但站在我們的立場，這是為了與各位合作所必要的手續。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "這點小事不會麻煩。不如說，能借用你們的力量讓我們很安心呢，聖德芬。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "在撒旦那起事件中受到你們幫助了。返還人情是當然的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我們天使與使徒全員保證，有必要時一定會盡力協助尤蒂爾。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_2080.wav"], "content": "謝謝妳。那麼再次，今後也請妳多多指教了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "接下來，為了答謝妳特地遠道而來，請接受我們的款待吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "請別介意。輔佐組織運作是我的職責。與各地聯繫也是常有的事，不必特地慰勞。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "比起這個，希望能讓我視察這座聖城。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "經由使徒們的報告獲得的片斷情報，我認為這是個親眼確認的好機會。是否能請你允准？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗯，當然。那麼克菈兒，拜託妳為她帶路了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "原來如此。確實和報告中相同，這座城裡住著不同種族、出身的人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "是啊。城裡有許多人因欣賞尤蒂爾的為人，而聚集到這裡。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……只是，當中也有些人讓人頗傷腦筋──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110009_story/VO_CHR_110009_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "呀啊啊──！？我、我又失敗了！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "筱婭", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "啊啊！？我才剛說完，筱婭就……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "聖德芬小姐，抱歉嚇到妳了……！剛才的爆炸在聖城是常有的事，並不是什麼敵襲……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "不必擔心。我已從使徒的報告得知，這座城裡會發生因時空物理魔法實驗失敗而引發的爆炸。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "原、原來如此……那就好。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……不過，儘管早就預料到，卻能完全不為所動。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（多麼冷靜啊……該說不愧能負責統率眾天使嗎……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "……好，我們剛才大致走過了聖城比較有名的地方，妳覺得如何呢？希望能讓妳滿意。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不，還不夠。我希望能對機密技術進行視察。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_1008.wav"], "content": "機、機密技術……！？那究竟、是指什麼呢……！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "使徒們曾向我報告說，這裡的某個人持有稀有道具。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "想請妳為我介紹那個道具的持有人。那人名叫──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110316_story/VO_CHR_110316_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "預備──八千五百一十二，四千零三十……逢一進一逢二進二！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110316_01.png", "speakerName": "小蕾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0017.wav"], "content": "太棒了。令人驚嘆的計算速度。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_1079.wav"], "content": "原來如此……聖德芬小姐的目的，原來是算盤啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "正是。若能提升計算速度，對我平時的工作也有幫助。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "指揮組織，等同調動數字。管理帳簿是我的工作。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110316_story/VO_CHR_110316_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "哎呀，這樣啊。呵呵，我們似乎很合得來呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110316_01.png", "speakerName": "小蕾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "身為被指派負責管理聖城的人，我也非常能理解聖德芬小姐的辛苦……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "如果有什麼能做的事，我們會不遺餘力幫忙的。對吧，小蕾小姐？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110316_story/VO_CHR_110316_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "嗯，當然了。聖德芬小姐，備用的算盤就請妳拿去吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110316_01.png", "speakerName": "小蕾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0061.wav"], "content": "這倒不必。只要能理解算盤的構造及用法就夠了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？是這樣嗎……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "是的。我們與各位所締結的，是面對戰略性威脅時的同盟協定。當中不包含物資往來。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "更何況我們的指揮官柯恩，是「道具」方面的專家。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0083.wav"], "content": "──以上就是關於算盤的概要。我想委託妳重現這個道具。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "傳自東方陶國的計算工具……是嗎。好吧，似乎很有趣。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不過話說回來還真難得，妳竟然會有事拜託我。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……經妳如此一說，確實。這是第一次。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "嗯，我是完全無所謂啦。只要有了算盤，確實能在工作上提供妳很大的幫助。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0071.wav"], "content": "那麼，妳就放一百二十個心等著吧。我會做出超乎妳想像的東西的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "……對指揮官的拜託、嗎。雖然試著回溯更久以前的記憶，卻沒有相應的例子。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "明明侍奉梅塔特隆數百年期間都不曾有過，為什麼……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110396011, "title": "沉著冷靜的五大天使司令"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "這是妳想要的算盤的試作。覺得如何？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "謝謝妳。不過，和我在聖城看見的形狀有點不同呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "只是單純做相同的東西太無趣了。想說機會難得，所以我嘗試進行了改良。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我覺得這個叫「算盤」的道具，雖然能快速計算，但無法直接以數字顯示結果這點相當不便。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "因此，我嘗試將它連上我的平板，藉以將計算結果顯示在上面。像這樣。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "喔，確實很便利。看來帳簿管理能輕鬆許多。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "呵呵，我的發明似乎對妳的工作有所幫助，太好了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那麼，為了能更提升工作效率，我想拜託妳追加一些功能。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0063.wav"], "content": "除了顯示計算結果外，我希望還能加以記錄，辦得到嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "呵。我就猜妳會這麼說，所以已經加上記錄功能了。我可是毫無遺漏的喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0017.wav"], "content": "真令人驚訝，不愧是柯恩。謝謝妳。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──喔，帳簿管理竟然這麼快就結束了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "相較以前，作業時間直接減半嗎。算盤的確實現了工作效率化的效果呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "天使雷米爾，現在歸隊。……哎呀，妳手上的道具很少見呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "這叫作「算盤」，是傳自東方的計算工具。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210154_story/VO_DRG_210154_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "喔，是算盤啊！這麼說來我在旅途中有見過呢！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210154_01.png", "speakerName": "拉斐爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……咦？不過，算盤是長這個樣子的嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210154_01.png", "speakerName": "拉斐爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "柯恩進行過改良。能顯示計算結果，並加以記錄。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "已經可說是與算盤不同東西。稱之為新發明也不為過。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210154_story/VO_DRG_210154_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "原來如此。柯恩還是老樣子，真的很能幹耶。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210154_01.png", "speakerName": "拉斐爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210145_story/VO_DRG_210145_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "就是啊。她製作的方便道具，幫了我們很多忙呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210145_01.png", "speakerName": "加百列", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "的確。雖然以前也曾有過很能幹的指揮官，但柯恩尤其特別。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "聰明伶俐，研究上的表現也十分優秀。彷彿就像我們天使之長──梅塔特隆。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "柯恩的才能，確實與已逝的梅塔特隆有共通之處呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "例如天使間的通訊原本是由梅塔特隆創造出的秘術，柯恩卻以煉金術做到相近的程度。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210154_story/VO_DRG_210154_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "那個真的很厲害耶！多虧那個，才讓大家從一盤散沙的狀態下成功逆轉！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210154_01.png", "speakerName": "拉斐爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210145_story/VO_DRG_210145_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "她下達的指示也很準確呢。預測結果精準得就像能看見未來一樣。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210145_01.png", "speakerName": "加百列", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210154_story/VO_DRG_210154_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "然後回過神來，戰況已經在不知不覺間倒向我們……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210154_01.png", "speakerName": "拉斐爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "呵呵。說不定啊，柯恩比梅塔特隆更適合當領導者呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210145_01.png", "speakerName": "加百列", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "梅塔特隆作為我們天使的領導者，有點太強勢了對吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210145_01.png", "speakerName": "加百列", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210154_story/VO_DRG_210154_STORY_0013.wav"], "content": "就是說啊！雖然要說是靠得住也沒錯，但感覺好像都讓那傢伙負責就夠了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210154_01.png", "speakerName": "拉斐爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "重要的事完全不告訴任何人，什麼都只想自己處理。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210154_01.png", "speakerName": "拉斐爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我記得，1000年前與撒旦的決戰，最後也是由梅塔特隆和撒旦單獨對決。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "就這點而言，我想柯恩很清楚與他人合作的重要性喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "同意。柯恩的資質，並不輸給梅塔特隆。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "她那超乎常人的才能不僅是使徒，就算成為我們天使的領導者也無可挑剔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210154_01.png", "speakerName": "天使們", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "嗯？怎麼了？如果有什麼意見，直說無妨。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210154_story/VO_DRG_210154_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "沒有啦，該說是意見、還是感想……只是看到妳相當信任柯恩，嚇了一跳而已。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210154_01.png", "speakerName": "拉斐爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210145_story/VO_DRG_210145_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "是啊……因為聖德芬不太會將想法說出口……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210145_01.png", "speakerName": "加百列", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗯，雖然我能大致感覺到妳的想法，但像現在這樣聽見妳親自說出口，會讓我們比較安心呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "我明白了。若各位如此期望，那我就重新將想法告訴你們吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我認為柯恩是歷代中資質最傑出的指揮官，我十分期待她未來的表現。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "由於撒旦復活，導致葛拉姆斯、教會，以及我們都受到相當嚴重的損害。但是，不必擔心。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只要有柯恩這名值得信賴的指揮官，我相信一定能跨越這次的艱難局面。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "……原來如此，這就是妳的想法嗎。看來妳們之間有著超乎我想像的深厚信賴呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "這點本身並不是壞事……然而，感情有時會讓判斷變得遲鈍。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "過度的期待一旦出錯將變為盲目相信。請妳，務必留意。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "當然。我對柯恩的評價，是基於客觀事實，其中並不包含私人情感。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "……那我就安心了。看來是多餘的操心呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……但是，我總是不禁認為，聖德芬似乎過於在柯恩身上尋找梅塔特隆的影子……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（但願只是我太杞人憂天就好……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110396012, "title": "柯恩的發明"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "那天，使徒與天使們全員出動，前去執行某個重要任務。", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "──專心聆聽。本次作戰目標，是解放被鄰國占據的村落，並拯救被劫為人質的伊利亞教祭司們。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "諸位從村落四方一口氣進攻。拯救祭司們的同時殲滅敵軍吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "關於進攻的時機，之後會再指示。各自於指定位置等候指令。以上。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0080.wav"], "content": "已經向使徒們傳達作戰內容。號令就拜託妳了，柯恩。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "柯恩？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……啊啊，抱歉。聯絡辛苦妳了，聖德芬。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "真是的，才想著解決了撒旦的事，馬上換鄰國跑來侵略嗎。連喘口氣的時間都沒有。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "敵人就是盯上這一點吧。葛拉姆斯因為撒旦造成的損害相當疲乏，是進攻的好時機。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "是沒錯。實際上國境附近的村落也是這麼輕易就落到了敵人手中。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……不過，對方再猖狂也已到此為止。為了本次作戰，我還準備了一個「秘策」。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0086.wav"], "content": "葛拉姆斯的伊利亞加護仍然健在──奉神之威名讓他們體會一下吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "──報告。全員，各就各位。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0082.wav"], "content": "好，告訴使徒與天使們。作戰開始！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──涅因與雷米爾已經遇敵。請求指示。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "直接開始交戰。只要能撐一陣子，琵儂、加百列就會跟他們會合對敵方發動夾擊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "了解。我來傳達。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──涅因他們與琵儂等人會合。採取夾擊攻破敵人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（柯恩的戰術果然很優秀。雖然人待在這裡，卻完美掌握了遠方戰場的情勢。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "柯恩？怎麼了，請求下一個指示。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "……嗯？啊啊，抱歉。請涅因與琵儂他們在發出下一個指示前，先在原地等候指令。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……在必須爭分奪秒的戰況下等候指令嗎。雖然覺得有點太過悠哉，但柯恩的話應該是有什麼想法吧。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "了解。我來傳達。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……奇怪。命令涅因他們等候指令之後，就沒有發出任何指示。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（以作戰而言，等候指令的時間長得太不自然。以防萬一，是否該向柯恩確認想法？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──是拉斐爾啊。怎麼了？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "……！了解。我立刻轉告柯恩，請求指示。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "發生什麼事了？感覺不是什麼好消息……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "理薩和拉斐爾被敵軍包圍，目前正陷入苦戰。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "什麼！？奇怪……涅因他們現在在做什麼？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……？涅因跟琵儂他們的話，還在持續等候指令。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "妳說什麼！？我應該有指示他們在等候指令後，就觀察時機和理薩會合啊！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "……與事實不符。柯恩並沒有下達那樣的指示。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0035.wav"], "content": "沒有下達指示！？怎麼可能──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不，等等……我以為我有發出指示，但那該不會……是在做夢嗎……！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "抱歉……！這是我的疏失！我實在沒臉面對大家……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "總之現在得先解決理薩遇到的危機！轉告他們使用「秘策」！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "了解──理薩、拉斐爾。允許使用「那個道具」。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "以煉金術做出的藥物製成的「麻痺煙霧」。趁它讓敵方無力化的期間重整態勢吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "之後柯恩的指示相當精確，作戰順利進行，最終成功解救了村落。", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0048.wav"], "content": "真的非常抱歉。因為我的疏失，給各位造成這麼大的麻煩……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "要求說明。我不認為柯恩會忘記下達指示。應該有什麼理由不是嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "……應該是因為、疲勞吧。為了開發「麻痺煙霧」熬了兩天夜，沒想到意外地勞累。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這次作戰，如果敵方將人質當成盾，我們將會束手無策。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "所以我想應該需要能在守護人質的同時讓敵方無力化的無殺傷力武器，才急忙進行開發，但……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "沒想到會因為疲勞而遺漏下達重要的指示。根本是本末倒置。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "……原來如此，原因我理解了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這次的事我正在深刻反省。等使徒們回來之後，我會好好向大家道歉的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……那麼，我先走了。雖然很抱歉，但讓我稍微睡一下吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "……看來，我不得不承認雷米爾的擔心是對的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "或許因為我過於期待柯恩能成為梅塔特隆第二，而給予了超出客觀事實的評價。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "如果是梅塔特隆，無論進行多麼長時間的秘術研究，都不曾對思考造成影響。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "這是人類的極限。也就代表她果然無法代替梅塔特隆吧。非常遺憾，柯恩……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110396013, "title": "人類的極限"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "我前來拿取資料了。請問準備好了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "是的。本月聖城的活動紀錄在這裡。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "……已確認。沒問題。給妳添麻煩了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那麼，我先告辭。因為我還有其他工作要做。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "那真是可惜……我原本打算請妳享用蜂蜜蛋糕的呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "什麼？妳說蜂蜜蛋糕？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "是的。我聽說聖德芬小姐很喜歡蜂蜜，所以特地事先做好等妳來。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0066.wav"], "content": "……妳說的蛋糕，請讓我嚐嚐吧。重新省視行程的結果，應該可以擠出一些時間享用輕食。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0068.wav"], "content": "非常美味。蜂蜜的味道濃厚而豐潤，太棒了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "呵呵，看來妳很中意聖城特製的蜂蜜，真是太好了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0064.wav"], "content": "什麼？這是在這座城裡採到的嗎？實在太令人驚嘆了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "我想應該是因為這片土地充滿了高純度的瑪納吧，所以才能採到品質優良的蜂蜜。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "原來如此。確實能從這片土地感受到特別的瑪納。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "像這樣的地方，世界上僅有此處。能找到這裡的阿爾博流斯陛下真的很厲害呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "阿爾博流斯嗎。記得他是一位在南格拉斯迪亞大陸名留青史的英雄吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "是的。他是在300年前建立阿爾貝利亞王國的建國君王……也是我最初侍奉的主人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我300年來一直守著這座城……然後，才和新的主人尤蒂爾相遇。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這樣啊。原來克菈兒從過去到現在曾有過兩位主人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "阿爾博流斯與尤蒂爾。建國英雄，與身為其後裔的王子。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……克菈兒。我能請教妳一件事嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "嗯？什麼事呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "克菈兒曾經比較過過去與現在的主人嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "具體而言，例如期待尤蒂爾能成為阿爾博流斯第二之類的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "這個嘛……一開始的時候，或許多多少少會吧。況且他們兩位都是複龍契約者。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但是，現在我已經不會再拿他們兩位做比較了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……理由是？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "因為陛下有陛下的優點，而王子有王子的優點。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "阿爾博流斯陛下十分強大，獨自背負大家的希望，站得比任何人都前面，總是在最前線戰鬥。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "而尤蒂爾則性格溫柔、為他人著想，能和大家攜手團結向前……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "他們兩位之間的不同，是無法比較出優劣的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（阿爾博流斯與尤蒂爾……兩者關係，跟梅塔特隆與柯恩很像。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（偉大的先人，與其繼承者。但是，兩者都擁有各自的優點，無法比較。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……克菈兒說得沒錯。我過度期望柯恩能變得跟梅塔特隆一模一樣了。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "……原來如此，我理解了。謝謝妳寶貴的意見。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "不用客氣。似乎有幫上妳的忙，我很高興。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……回想起來，我剛遇見王子那陣子，也對與他之間的距離感到困惑。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我明明是名僕從，卻與王子平起平坐，有時甚至會嚴厲地責罵王子……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不過，後來我才明白，那令人感覺親近的氣質正是尤蒂爾擁有的魅力。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "彼此扶持、互相依賴……和我侍奉陛下的時候，是完全不同的充實感。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "感覺親近……彼此扶持……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0071.wav"], "content": "那麼，妳就放一百二十個心等著吧。我會做出超乎妳想像的東西的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "……對指揮官的拜託、嗎。雖然試著回溯更久以前的記憶，卻沒有相應的例子。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "明明侍奉梅塔特隆數百年期間都不曾有過，為什麼……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……我懂了。為什麼我，會只拜託柯恩事情。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（因為我和柯恩在不知不覺間，已經成為彼此扶持的存在。而證據，就是當時──）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0063.wav"], "content": "除了顯示計算結果外，我希望還能加以記錄，辦得到嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "呵。我就猜妳會這麼說，所以已經加上記錄功能了。我可是毫無遺漏的喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（我跟柯恩會互相提出意見、彼此協助。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（也會為了達到目的聯手合作。這點正是梅塔特隆所沒有，但柯恩擁有的優點。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（若是如此，當時、我……！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_1010.wav"], "content": "那個、聖德芬小姐……？看妳一直不說話，怎麼了嗎……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "我要向妳道謝，克菈兒。托妳的福我才能正確地自我分析。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我必須向柯恩謝罪。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "當柯恩因疲勞忘記下達指示時，我該做的並非對她失望，而是其他事情……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110396014, "title": "兩位主人"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "帳簿管理完畢。接下來是確認報告書吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（首先，得優先處理因外出而積累的雜務。之後再去向柯恩謝罪吧。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（可不能因為我個人的問題，疏忽原本應做的工作。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "……唔，這份報告書記載有遺漏呢。要退回給琵儂。然後──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0072.wav"], "content": "──好，雜務都解決了。這樣就能去向柯恩謝罪。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "這、是……身體站不穩……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "經過長距離的移動從聖城回來後，完全沒休息就著手處理雜務，而造成了超出預料的負擔嗎。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "沒辦法。暫且以休息為最優先吧。只要休息一下，馬上就能行……動……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "……嗯？這裡是柯恩的研究室？還有、這條毛毯是？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "妳醒了啊，聖德芬。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "柯恩，莫非毛毯是妳蓋的？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "嗯。在那種地方睡著，可是會感冒的喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "是嗎……謝謝妳為我擔心。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "從狀況來看，妳應該是不眠不休地處理完雜務後，一時放鬆才不小心睡著……沒錯吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "傷腦筋，工作狂也該有個限度。否則真的會弄壞身體喔？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "那些話，我要原封不動地還給妳。工作狂這點彼此彼此吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "呵，的確。畢竟我前幾天也因為疲勞，犯下了不該有的錯誤。那時候真的很抱歉。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "…………關於那件事，我也必須謝罪。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我早已察覺柯恩有可能忘記指示。但是，我卻疏於向柯恩確認。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "當時柯恩的過失，我本該有辦法事前預防的。今後我會注意不讓同樣情況發生。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "聖德芬……原來是這樣。妳察覺到了我的指示有異……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0017.wav"], "content": "妳果然很能幹呢。想到有妳當我的輔佐，實在很安心。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "因為我也並不完美。希望以後妳可以繼續支持我。……搭檔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……搭、檔……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "怎麼了？妳該不會不知道「搭檔」這個詞的意思吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0035.wav"], "content": "否定。我明白詞彙本身的意思。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只是，對這個詞彙出現在我與柯恩的關係上感到意外。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "嗯。既然如此，就趁這個機會修改妳的認知吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我跟妳，是彼此扶持、互相依賴的關係。世間一般都將這種關係稱為搭檔喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "彼此扶持、互相依賴……和我侍奉陛下的時候，是完全不同的充實感。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……原來如此。我能體會克菈兒那些話的意思了。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（這股胸中的溫暖，是我和梅塔特隆在一起時從未有過的。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（這就是、充實感嗎……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0044.wav"], "content": "──是雷米爾嗎。怎麼了？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……！了解。我來傳達。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "柯恩。緊急事件。根據收到的報告，莉莉斯現身於聖都葛拉姆斯附近。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110395_story/VO_CHR_110395_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "妳說什麼！？那個惡魔，竟然還沒學乖……這次一定要打倒她！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "要開始忙起來囉……！聖德芬，拜託妳輔佐我吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110395_01.png", "speakerName": "柯恩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0071.wav"], "content": "我明白了。包在我身上。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "身為妳的搭檔，我將會傾盡全力完成職責的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110396_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110396015, "title": "初次的鼓動"}]